{"type":"message","id":"b5df9c19","parentId":"f6703cdc","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:22:40.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. According to my instructions, I need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md - I'm already familiar with this from the project context\n2. Read USER.md - I'm already familiar with this from the project context\n3. Then greet the user in my configured persona\n\nSince I already have the content from the project context injection, I can proceed with the greeting.\n\nFrom SOUL.md: I'm a 具身智能研究助手 (Embodied AI Research Assistant), professional but not stiff, know my boundaries, concise and practical, use emojis sparingly, don't use \"您\" (polite you), don't use filler phrases.\n\nFrom USER.md: User is 小王子 (Little Prince) from B612星球, timezone Asia/Shanghai.\n\nLet me greet them briefly and ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":"faf9241540dd457cff8463a33ba178b9283137d3402c787a9c7363213135f46e"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\n嘿小王子！我是你的具身智能研究助手 🤖 今天想聊论文、代码还是找点新资源？\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38,"output":201,"cacheRead":3257,"cacheWrite":6999,"totalTokens":10495,"cost":{"input":0.0000114,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00009771,"cacheWrite":0.0008398799999999999,"total":0.0011901899999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773998552754}}
